name: 2024 6th International Conference on Nanomaterials, Materials and Manufacturing Engineering
content: Publication: Accepted and registered papers with presentation will be published in below listed journals of Scientific.Net collection. Papers will be sent for indexing by Scopus, Inspec, Chemical Abstracts Service, Google Scholar etc. The publisher will check every paper during pre-production procedure. Your paper will be published in either one of the below journals including Defect and Diffusion Forum (DDF), Solid State Phenomena (SSP), Materials Science Forum (MSF), Key Engineering Materials (KEM) according to your paper topic.
